  })), mdx("li", {
    parentName: "ul"
  }, "And this is exactly why we are so grateful for tech companies like Google, Slack and Zoom who make it easy for people with great ideas, great perspectives and great communication abilities, to deliver value to the world in a regenerative way.", mdx("span", {
