  }, "You might be a great teacher, but if you have to work in a physical school, you are going to be limited by the physical resources at your disposal; your energy, your time, your classes, your salary, your health, your enthusiasm, your travel time and cost, and then the travel time and cost of all your students...", mdx("span", {
