  }, "(The question \u2018how does this bring greater life to all?\u2019 should be the fundamental driver of all \u2018business\u2019 practices, and it should be the fundamental driver of any organisation setting out to make a difference. It\u2019s not about making a difference for ourselves, for our families, our communities, our relatives - it\u2019s about making a difference for every person alive on the planet and all future living humans.)", mdx("span", {
